00:28:22.610 --> 00:28:25.950
But OK, so you
have this behavior.

00:28:25.950 --> 00:28:28.080
And then what we
haven't established

00:28:28.080 --> 00:28:31.440
and the reason that I'm still
doing all of this algebra

00:28:31.440 --> 00:28:34.850
is that, OK, this
curve is going up,

00:28:34.850 --> 00:28:37.990
where is it going to end up?

00:28:37.990 --> 00:28:40.540
Is it going to
end up here, here,

00:28:40.540 --> 00:28:43.790
or right where this curve hits?

00:28:43.790 --> 00:28:45.080
OK?

00:28:45.080 --> 00:28:48.180
And what I will show
you is that this

00:28:48.180 --> 00:28:54.290
